base stats:
    health (HP)
    * health regenerates only through sleeping overnight or through monster drops
    stamina (SP)
    * stamina regenerates slowly when walking or quickly when standing still, but only if your FP are non-zero
    * they also are boosted to 100% when switching screens
    magic (MP)
    * magic regenerates to full every time you switch screens
    guts (GP)
    * guts regenerates only through sleeping overnight at >= half health and >= half food points.
        and only one at a time.

hidden stats:
    food points (FP)
    * hidden from user, these refill only when you eat.
    * they decrease to refill up the stamina and magic meters

